OL,3,CCouple travel to wedding on Metro
OL,4,Cafter being inspired by social media
OL,6,FA couple from Gateshead travelled on
OL,7,Fthe Tyne and Wear Metro to their
OL,8,Fwedding inspired by a social media
OL,9,Ftrend.
OL,11,FLaura and Aaron Capon saw couples in
OL,12,FNew York swap traditional cars for the
OL,13,Fsubway system to travel to their
OL,14,Fwedding venues. They caught the Metro
OL,15,Ffrom Gateshead to Haymarket for their
OL,16,Fceremony at Newcastle Civic Centre.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
