PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780503064
OL,3,CCouple travel to wedding on Metro
OL,4,Cafter being inspired by social media
OL,6,FLaura, 33, filmed the journey for
OL,7,Fsocial media. She said: "It was really
OL,8,Fgood fun getting the Metro to our
OL,9,Fwedding. We both loved it. It is
OL,10,Fsomething a bit different.
OL,12,F"I had seen the trend over in New York
OL,13,Fwhere couples are swapping the more
OL,14,Fpicture-perfect settings for the
OL,15,Fsubway, and in some cases, they
OL,16,Factually get married on the train. We
OL,17,Freally wanted to recreate that, but on
OL,18,Four own Metro system here.
OL,26,@oD@YOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
