OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780503064
OL,3,CCouple travel to wedding on Metro
OL,4,Cafter being inspired by social media
OL,6,F"I wanted the most Newcastle way
OL,7,Fpossible to get married, so the Metro
OL,8,Freally had to play a part in the day.
OL,10,F"We opted to travel to and from the
OL,11,Fregister office with just our
OL,12,Fvideographer in tow. A few passengers
OL,13,Fwere coming over to say
OL,14,Fcongratulations, which was lovely. I
OL,15,Feven had messages from people after
OL,16,Fthe wedding saying that they had seen
OL,17,Fus on the train. It really was a case
OL,18,Fof from the Metro to matrimony."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUzD@`O]
