PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780503064
OL,3,CCouple travel to wedding on Metro
OL,4,Cafter being inspired by social media
OL,6,FHer husband, Aaron, 34, said: "I loved
OL,7,Fgetting the Metro to the wedding. It
OL,8,Fwas a memorable experience.
OL,10,F"It was a Friday morning so there were
OL,11,Fstill people on the train heading to
OL,12,Fwork and university. It brought a
OL,13,Fsmile to people's faces. We were in
OL,14,Four own little bubble that morning,
OL,15,Fbut it was great that so many people
OL,16,Fcame over and said we had helped to
OL,17,Fmake their day."
OL,26,@nD@_OUrD@AOUyD@PO]
