PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780503064
OL,3,CCouple travel to wedding on Metro
OL,4,Cafter being inspired by social media
OL,6,FLynne Dickinson, Station Delivery
OL,7,FManager at Nexus, said: "It was great
OL,8,Fto welcome Laura and Aaron on board on
OL,9,Ftheir wedding day. The new Metro
OL,10,Ftrains were a perfect way to travel.
OL,12,F"It was a short trip from Gateshead to
OL,13,FHaymarket, but it certainly caught the
OL,14,Fattention of other customers, who all
OL,15,Flooked thrilled. Our heartfelt
OL,16,Fcongratulations to the happy couple
OL,17,Fand we wish them every health
OL,18,Fhappiness for their future together as
OL,19,Fman and wife."
OL,26,@oD@YOUtD@AOU{D@NO]
